data.description: Located on a corner lot, this charming ranch home features 3 bedrooms, 2 1/2 bathrooms, an attached 2 car garage, an airy and expansive living room adorned with a bay window, an updated eat-in kitchen w/SS appliances, new ceramic tile floor (2019), newer garbage disposal (2017). The fully finished basement includes a family room with a stunning floor-to-ceiling fireplace with elegant finishes, dry-bar, 1/2 bathroom, large laundry room, and a versatile bonus room suitable for use as an office, den, or playroom! The spacious fenced backyard with a patio is ideal for entertaining, featuring amenities like a gazebo, shed, and playset for the kids! New roof- 2019 New siding-2020 New fence-2021. Fantastic location surrounded by parks and playgrounds! Conveniently located near schools, restaurants, shopping, and with easy access to highways. SELLER IS HIGHLY MOTIVATED TO SELL AND WE ARE OPEN TO REVIEWING ALL OFFERS. SELLER IS OFFERING A CINCH HOME WARRANTY AS PART OF THE PURCHASE. THE HOME IS BEING SOLD AS IS.
